code: @Override protected Endpoint createEndpoint(String uri, String remaining, Map<String, Object> parameters) throws Exception {     CaffeineConfiguration configuration = this.configuration.copy().     setProperties(configuration, parameters).     return new CaffeineLoadCacheEndpoint(uri, this, remaining, configuration). }
